segue_dave.line: Massive Attack arranged their song "Inertia Creeps (Manic Street Preachers version)", and Manic Street Preachers remixed the same song...
segue_dave.explanation: Massive Attack arranged the song Inertia Creeps (Manic Street Preachers version), while Manic Street Preachers remixed the song Inertia Creeps (Manic Street Preachers version).
